ActCustoms Tariff
SubjectFerry-Boats, Tankers and Cargo Vessels Remission Order, 2010
PrecisFERRY-BOATS, TANKERS AND CARGO VESSELS REMISSION ORDER, 2010, in order to put into place a new customs duty remission framework for all cargo vessels and tankers, as well as ferries of a length of 129 metres or more, permanently imported into Canada for the first time, as of January 1, 2010.
